input_str:
1 Don't go looking for fights. Do everything you can to avoid them.

2 Know your own limitations. If you can't go thirty seconds without stopping for breath start working out and getting some endurance training. You need to be able to last a good three minutes of solid fighting/grappling/wrestling.

3 Fight like your life depends on it. No one fights to get the other person to submit. You fight to hurt people. Do you want to get hurt or go home safely?

4 Stay
